FBIS4-28996 "dreas115_n_94009" FBIS-EAS-94-115 Daily Report 13 Jun 1994 Vietnam World Bank Grants Agriculture Loan World Bank Grants Agriculture Loan BK1406071294 Hanoi Voice of Vietnam in English 1000 GMT 13 Jun 94 BK1406071294 Hanoi Voice of Vietnam English BFN [Text] Ten Vietnamese Southern peasant cities have received loans valued at $52 million from the World Bank to restore agriculture. The loans are aimed at restoring and developing agricultural services, giving financial credit to 50,000 farmer households, and restoring 150,000 hectares of rubber trees. They also help Vietnam provide trends and pioneer projects on the development of rural areas.
